            India's Signature Bridge a big draw for selfie-seekers
            The Signature Bridge in India's capital city, Delhi, is just a few weeks old. But it has already become notorious for drawing selfie-seekers who climb onto its cables to get the perfect shot.Video by Vikrant Singh, Piyush Nagpal and Nikita Mandhani
                
